Hey Guys,

Recently we learned a a lot about International Justice Mission. My friend from Chi Alpha is putting on a Lip Sync Battle to help raise awareness and fight against human trafficking. You guys should definitely check this event out, plus I'm Emceeing this event, so that's even more of a reason to come. Hope to see you all tomorrow Night!
